r. F. No, no, no, it's - you know - most of the - especially the young folk - used to - to go away for seasonal work, especially to the east coast, Aberdeen, and - Wick and Buckie, to the - to the - to the fishing, herring fishing. Now - there was - used 
to be in the - in the militia, young boys, Seaforth and Cameron Highlanders. And - others used to be enrolled as \{BLANK\}
 reservists. Now, in winter - they - of - of course - they - they used to train in - Stornaway, in the old battery buildings there. And -
 it was then - that was - that would be about 19 - 19 - 06 or seven - the - they used to enrol them in Stornaway. But - things - must have changed - and they had to go to the South of England for their training. The - the - initial training was - three mo
n
ths abroad ship, Portsmouth, Sheerness and all - of the famous - Naval - places like that. Now - nearly everyone had different experience. So that a - apart from being interesting - it was very very - instructive because - all the - everything that happen
ed - somebody had - somebody had a good account of it. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14184279 K3  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9644372\charrsid11559355 Mrs. M. They all came home in the wintertime.</subject3>
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8197677 KF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9644372\charrsid11559355 Yes. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14184279 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9644372\charrsid11559355 Did they talk about politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8197677 KF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9644372\charrsid11559355 Yes, oh yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14184279 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9644372\charrsid11559355 Did your father take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8197677 KF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9644372\charrsid11559355 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14184279 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9644372\charrsid11559355 Was he a Liberal?
