 - changed everything. Up to that - the - most people - there - there was a lot of land anger here. People wanted to - to - wanted the farm to be broken up into - so that people would get homes and all that. Well the - this seemed to be a - a; tramcar wit
h candidates. Seeking - seeking election. Yes. That - that sort of thing.
